title: Chapel of the Diamond Beast
story: The chapel of the Diamond Beast is situated deep in the swamps, far from civilization. Currently it is overrun with rabbits.

notes.text: A great stone gate with a keyhole on the eastern wall.
A shield and a sword hidden in a crack of the wall.
A key locked in a magical safe.
A skeleton on the ground, answers one question if disturbed.
An uncanny, slightly glowing halberd in a medium strongbox.
